7800:[name]将軍[line]You have my thanks.[%p]
7900:Wait, something was wrong with this Shogun.[%p]
8000:Something was different than before. Right. His voice. His voice wasn't right.[%p]
8100:[name]拓巳[line]Your... voice.[%p]
8200:[name]将軍[line]A voice…[%p]
8300:[name]将軍[line]is just vibration in the air.[%p]
8400:[name]将軍[line]Any number of things can change how it sounds.[%p]
8500:[name]将軍[line]Am I wrong?[%p]
8600:What was going on? His voice was changing more and more.[%p]
8700:Was he using some kind of machine? Maybe he didn't want me to identify his voice? At this point, why bother?[%p]
8800:And what he was saying didn't make any sense, either.[%p]
8900:[name]星来[line]Takky, he's trying to confuse you![%p]
9000:[name]星来[line]Don't let your guard down! And don't listen to him![%p]
9100:T-That's right. Seira-tan was right.[%p]
9200:Seira-tan was always right. Always.[%p]
9300:I put my hand over the pocket I was keeping her in and squeezed tight.[%p]
9400:[name]拓巳[line]W-W-Where's... N-Nanami?[%p]
9500:I was so afraid, my heart felt like it was about to burst out of my mouth. I forced myself to speak anyway.[%p]
9600:I thought stuff like this only happened on TV and in video games.[%p]
9700:[name]拓巳[line]Is Nanami... already dead?[%p]
9800:[name]将軍[line]No.[%p]
9900:[name]星来[line]No way! He cut off her hand, right?[%p]
10000:[name]星来[line]Even if she is alive, she'll still die from blood loss any minute now![%p]
10100:I started to cry.[%p]
10200:I could see Nanami's puffed-up, pouting face in my mind.[%p]
10300:She was a little brat. Honestly, she was obnoxious.[%p]
10400:But still... I was so sad. So sad I was crying.[%p]
10500:[name]拓巳[line]Nanami... Nanami's my little sister. I cared about her.[%p]
10600:[name]拓巳[line]Why did you kill her? How could you?[%p]
10700:[name]将軍[line]You think she's dead?[%p]
10800:[name]将軍[line]That might've been somebody else's hand, you know.[%p]
10900:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?[%p]
11000:[name]将軍[line]The bangle and the phone might've been hers, but how do you know that wasn't somebody else's hand?[%p]
11100:Nanami was... alive?[%p]
11200:[name]星来[line]I'm telling you! Don't believe him![%p]
11300:[name]将軍[line]If you can finish the quest, I'll give her back.[%p]
11400:[name]将軍[line]I'll give her back to you, alive.[%p]
11500:Quest. There was that word again.[%p]
11600:Did he think this was a video game?[%p]
11700:But... but the real me wasn't a hero.[%p]
11800:[name]将軍[line]But if you fail the quest, she's never coming back.[%p]
11900:His voice suddenly grew as cold as a blade.[%p]
12000:I felt so stupid, being afraid of such an old man. But...[%p]
12100:He was… crazy. He was the NewGen killer.[%p]
12200:[name]将軍[line]So, make sure you finish the quest, and don't disappoint me.[%p]
12300:[name]将軍[line]I know you can do it.[%p]
12400:[name]拓巳[line]Why... Why me?[%p]
12500:[name]拓巳[line]It didn't have to... It didn't have to be me, right?[%p]
12600:[name]将軍[line]It has to be you.[%p]
12700:[name]拓巳[line]B-But why?[%p]
12800:[name]将軍[line]Because you were chosen.[%p]
12900:Chosen...[%p]
13000:[name]星来[line]Don't misunderstand him, Takky![%p]
13100:[name]星来[line]He means you were “chosen” to be the next victim![%p]
13200:I remembered the horrible fates that had befallen the other NewGen victims, and shivered.[%p]
13300:[name]将軍[line]You remember what happened this afternoon, right?[%p]
13400:[name]拓巳[line]A-Afternoon?[%p]
13500:[name]将軍[line]You saved Ayase Kishimoto at school.[%p]
13600:Shogun's email had talked about her attempted suicide. He must've been watching from somewhere.[%p]
13700:Or maybe he'd mind-controlled her into trying to commit suicide in the first place.[%p]
13800:[name]将軍[line]Ayase only survived because she landed on that flowerbed, correct?[%p]
13900:Shogun knew about the power I supposedly had.[%p]
14000:Nobody there had found anything strange in the slightest about that flowerbed.[%p]
14100:The only one who'd known what had happened was Sena. And Sena had said this to me:[%p]
14200:[name]セナ[line]It was your delusion, right?[%p]
14300:[name]星来[line]Takky! Try to make him think he's wrong![%p]
14400:T-That's right! It was possible that Shogun was only after me... only trying to kill me...[%p]
14500:because of this power he thought I had.[%p]
14600:If I told him I didn't have it, maybe he'd let me go.[%p]
14700:[name]拓巳[line]I don't... have the power you think I do.[%p]
14800:[name]将軍[line]Power? What power? I haven't used the word “power” a single time.[%p]
14900:Oh, crap.[%p]
15000:[name]星来[line]You don't have any power, Takky! You're just a creepy loser otaku! You don't have what it takes to be a hero! You're just a harmless dork who never leaves his room and jerks off to me all day! Am I wrong?[%p]
15100:She was right.[%p]
15200:I didn't have any power. That was just a stupid kid's fantasy.[%p]
15300:After all the things that Sena and Ayase had said, I'd started to believe it was real.[%p]
15400:But the two of them were clearly crazy.[%p]
15500:I was stupid to believe anything a crazy person said.[%p]
15600:Hadn't Rimi said it was all a delusion, anyway?[%p]
15700:[name]将軍[line]Why don't you tell me more?[%p]
15800:[name]将軍[line]About that flowerbed, for instance.[%p]
15900:[name]拓巳[line]D-Do you have any proof that I did it?[%p]
16000:[name]拓巳[line]I-I don't have the power to make flowerbeds appear out of nowhere.[%p]
16100:[name]将軍[line]So, the flowerbed appeared out of nowhere. Hmm...[%p]
16200:[name]将軍[line]Everyone else thought it was there from the very start.[%p]
16300:[name]将軍[line]But you, you're aware of the fact that it was never there.[%p]
16400:Uugh... I might've dug my own grave again.[%p]
16500:Wait, who was Shogun, anyway? If he knew what the other students and teachers were saying... had he been there to hear it from them?[%p]
16600:[name]拓巳[line]I-I don't have any power. I don't even know how I did it.[%p]
16700:[name]将軍[line]But you did it nonetheless. Your delusion became reality.[%p]
16800:[name]星来[line]Don't let him trick you![%p]
16900:[name]星来[line]Takky, do you feel like you really have that power?[%p]
17000:[name]星来[line]That stuff only happens in anime![%p]
17100:[name]星来[line]You live in the real world![%p]
17200:[name]星来[line]The flowerbed, the way Ayase split in two... Can you prove that they were real?[%p]
17300:[name]星来[line]You can't, can you?[%p]
17400:[name]星来[line]Did you touch Ayase when she split?[%p]
17500:I didn't.[%p]
17600:[name]星来[line]You might've just been seeing things.[%p]
17700:[name]星来[line]You were really freaked out then because the police and Yua were after you.[%p]
17800:Then what about the flowerbed?[%p]
17900:[name]星来[line]It's the same thing.[%p]
18000:[name]星来[line]The flowerbed was always there.[%p]
18100:[name]星来[line]When you went to school looking for Rimi, your head hurt and you could barely think.[%p]
18200:[name]星来[line]Before Ayase fell, did you really look and see if there wasn't a flowerbed there?[%p]
18300:[name]星来[line]Nobody else thought it was strange that a flowerbed just appeared out of nowhere.[%p]
18400:[name]星来[line]So how do you know it wasn't there from the start?[%p]
18500:[name]星来[line]You were just mistaken, Takky![%p]
18600:[name]星来[line]Don't let Shogun fool you![%p]
18700:[name]拓巳[line]The flowerbed was always there…[%p]
18800:I repeated what Seira-tan had said.[%p]
18900:[name]拓巳[line]I-I thought it wasn't there at first, but I was wrong.[%p]
19000:[name]拓巳[line]I-It was just a delusion my mind made up.[%p]
19100:[name]拓巳[line]L-Look... everyone said there was always a flowerbed there, right?[%p]
19200:[name]拓巳[line]I-It wasn't any kind of weird power or anything.[%p]
19300:[name]拓巳[line]I was just... wrong.[%p]
19400:[name]将軍[line]No. You have that power.[%p]
19500:[name]将軍[line]Am I wrong?[%p]
19600:[name]拓巳[line]I-I don't want to die.[%p]
19700:[name]将軍[line]Am I wrong?[%p]
19800:[name]拓巳[line]I-I don't know... Please don't kill me.[%p]
19900:[name]将軍[line]You should be more aware of the fact that you have a God-given power.[%p]
20000:[name]将軍[line]Your latent potential is unbelievable.[%p]
20100:[name]将軍[line]You can change the world.[%p]
20200:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]
20300:I wanted to go home. I wanted to go back to the Base and grind in ESO until I passed out from exhaustion.[%p]
20400:I wanted to leer at my Seira-tan figure and watch Blood Tune on an endless loop.[%p]
20500:That's all I ever wanted, so why…[%p]
20600:[name]星来[line]Takky, run…[%p]
20700:[name]星来[line]I'll stay with you forever.[%p]
20800:[name]星来[line]I'm the only person in the world who's on your side.[%p]
20900:[name]星来[line]So, let's go home. Cut off all contact with the 3D world and just live to have fun![%p]
21000:[name]将軍[line]Now, then, I think we've talked enough. It's time for you to begin your quest.[%p]
21100:[name]将軍[line]First, go somewhere you can get a good look at Scramble Crossing.[%p]
21200:[name]星来[line]You have to run! He's really going to kill you.[%p]
21300:[name]将軍[line]Did you not hear me?[%p]
21400:[name]将軍[line]I said go somewhere you can look down on Scramble Crossing.[%p]
21500:His voice was soft, but incredibly cold.[%p]
21600:There was a sharpness to it that made him impossible to disobey.[%p]
21700:[name]拓巳[line]W-What do you want?[%p]
21800:My legs were shaking, and I couldn't move. I wrapped my arms around myself and hugged tight.[%p]
21900:Should I do what he said? Or not? I didn't have it in me to even decide.[%p]
22000:[name]将軍[line]You're not going to do what I tell you?[%p]
22100:[name]将軍[line]If you don't, I can't guarantee what will happen to Nanami.[%p]
22200:[name]星来[line]She's already dead! You know it! It's too late to save her! You'll just die for no reason![%p]
22300:[name]拓巳[line]L-Let me hear... her voice.[%p]
22400:I squeaked out the words. But Shogun ignored me.[%p]
22500:[name]将軍[line]There's no reason for me to do that. You should think a little more about the situation you're in.[%p]
22600:Uugh...[%p]
22700:I...[%p]
22800:I didn't want to think about the chance that Nanami was dead. I didn't want to imagine her dead. It felt like if I imagined it, it might really happen.[%p]
22900:I gave in and moved somewhere where I could look down on Scramble Crossing.[%p]
23000:The ground around my feet was dark. It felt like I might trip if I wasn't careful.[%p]
23100:There was a clear acrylic board on the side of the roof facing Scramble Crossing, acting as a wall. It was about three stories high.[%p]
23200:When I got close to the wall, I could hear the chaos below me.[%p]
23300:There was a female voice that seemed much louder than the others. It was the one coming from the big TV.[%p]
23400:[name]将軍[line]There's an open space in the wall. Do you see it?[%p]
23500:I looked at the wall, wiping away the heavy sweat on my forehead. He was right. There was a hole big enough for a single person to pass through.[%p]
23600:It was a strange shape, like it had been smashed open. Someone had clearly done it deliberately.[%p]
23700:Of course, there was nothing on the other side. It was a sheer drop off an eight-story building.[%p]
23800:[name]将軍[line]Peek out and say hello to the crowd below.[%p]
23900:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?![%p]
24000:What... What had he just said?[%p]
24100:[name]将軍[line]Do I need to tell you again?[%p]
24200:[name]将軍[line]Lean out from the hole and wave to the people.[%p]
24300:H-He couldn't mean…[%p]
24400:[name]星来[line]See? He's going to kill you![%p]
24500:I gulped. Is that how he'd made five people jump to their deaths?[%p]
24600:Seira-tan was right after all.[%p]
24700:I had no choice left but to die. I had to jump.[%p]
24800:[name]拓巳[line]N-No... No...[%p]
24900:[name]将軍[line]If you don't, Nanami will die.[%p]
25000:[name]星来[line]If you do, you'll die![%p]
25100:What was I supposed to do?[%p]
25200:I tried to think of my best option, but with every thought I had, the worst-case scenario came to me in the form of a delusion.[%p]
25300:Somebody, save me.[%p]
25400:[name]七海[line]Brother, you jerk.[%p]
25500:Nanami's voice echoed in my panicked ears.[%p]
25600:[name]七海[line]Heheh. Jerk.[%p]
25700:I could see her smiling in my mind.[%p]
25800:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]
25900:It was my fault. Nanami had nothing to do with any of this. But Shogun had kidnapped her because of me, and even cut off her arm.[%p]
26000:I'm sorry, Nanami... I'm sorry.[%p]
26100:I wiped the tears away. They came back, and I wiped them away again.[%p]
26200:And then, with blurry vision, I slowly walked to the hole,[%p]
26300:and gingerly peered out over the edge.[%p]
26400:There was a sudden cheer below me. It was so loud, it sounded like an earthquake.[%p]
26500:That big crowd in front of the station… and the media, too...[%p]
26600:They were all here for some event that was about to start.[%p]
26700:Suddenly a bright light assaulted me. I narrowed my eyes and looked away.[%p]
26800:I could see the big TV on the next building over. And the person on it was...[%p]
26900:Me.[%p]
27000:Huh? Me?[%p]
27100:The big TV showed me with my face covered in tears, and my mouth wide open like an idiot. Even my posture looked terrible.[%p]
27200:At first, I thought I was seeing things.[%p]
27300:And then next, I thought that somebody was secretly recording me, and I shivered.[%p]
27400:I even thought that maybe it was an image that Shogun was stealing from my mind.[%p]
27500:And finally...
27600: I realized that it was video of me, being taken right this very moment.[%p]
27700:And finally… I realized that it was video of me, being taken right this very moment.
27800:There was text in large letters running across the bottom of the screen.[%p]
27900:LIVE FROM SHIBUYA STATION! “THE AMAZING PSYCHIC BOY!”[%p]
28000:More text was scrolling beneath it.[%p]
28100:“AN EMERGENCY LIVE APPEARANCE OF A PSYCHIC BOY PERSONALLY VOUCHED FOR BY YURI BRIGHTMAN, THE GREATEST PSYCHIC OF THE 21ST CENTURY!” “WILL HE USE HIS POWERS TO FIND THE NEWGEN KILLER?!”[%p]
28200:Finally, I understood.[%p]
28300:The media and the gawkers in Scramble Crossing were all looking... at me.[%p]
28400:[margin top="266"][center]—Don't look at me.[unk19 index="0"]
28500:Why are they all looking at me? Psychic boy? What the heck?[%p]
28600:Didn't they all know what had happened today?[%p]
28700:There was an earthquake! It was an intensity five quake! Over 100 people died![%p]
28800:So... Why... were they all...[%p]
28900:getting excited over a weird loser like me?[%p]
